item.title: MAPLECTF 2023: JUJUTSU KAISEN
item.description: MapleCTF’s 2nd annual CTF was held at the same time as Hackceler8 weekend, so for a brief couple of days in Japan I was busy helping organize 2 ctfs at once, which I don’t reccommend. This year, I decided to spice things up with my chals, my vie chals, by incorporating a fun prize for whichever team manages to solve all of my challenges.I had 3 challenges: JaVieScript, Blade Runner, and Jujutsu Kaisen.
